data.description: Motivated Seller! What an amazing value to get into this Premier Neighborhood with beautiful homes, a busy neighborhood social calendar and so many ways to spend your leisure time. This home has been very well maintained and updated where it matters most. Picture entertaining in this Beautifully Updated kitchen with Quartz Countertops including a Waterfall End. The kitchen is Open to the family room with plenty of gathering space, Soaring 2 Story Ceiling and tons of natural light. Holiday meals fit perfectly in the generously sized dining room. The main floor has a great Guest Bedroom with its own private bathroom to welcome out of town visitors. Upstairs is the beautiful Master Bedroom with trey ceilings and updated Master Bathroom. Across the hall are two more bedrooms with a shared bathroom. An additional room upstairs works great as a home office or 5th bedroom. A full unfinished basement gives an overflow of storage or future potential! Just imagine what you could do!  New HVAC systems! Both upstairs and main level systems have been replaced. New Water Heater! Newer carpet with upgraded pad. The Leaf Guard Gutters include a transferable Lifetime Warranty. You'll love to call this neighborhood home. So many amenities! Neighborhood Park with a paved walking trail and picnic pavilion. Beautiful Golf course. Golf Cart Parades. Neighborhood pool. Tennis and Pickleball Courts. Come fall in love today!
